Introduction
============

It is a bash sctip to fetch yum updates and notifiy Sugar Shell.

While working, script will create log in /var/log/dextrose-updater and
/var/lib/dextrose-updater stamp file for checking update on daily basis.

Download
========

http://download.sugarlabs.org/sources/external/dextrose-updater/

Or checkout sources for read-only usage:

``git clone git://git.sugarlabs.org/dextrose-updater/mainline.git dextrose-updater``
